description: The Wrangler Lasso Vintage Crew is a limited edition made in USA pocket tee featuring the signature Roark x Wrangler 'Out Of Range' graphic, which pays homage to our time spent exploring our backyard and the century old legacy that Wrangler has built. This vintage tee is a heavier weight, pigment dyed and washed crew for a broken in look and feel.
name: Roark Wrangler Lasso Vintage Crew Premium Tee
